1182
01:21:33,173 --> 01:21:35,963
No!
McCarthy, you shit!

1183
01:21:38,390 --> 01:21:41,075
<i>The girls all know the score.</i>

1184
01:21:42,197 --> 01:21:47,472
<i>No escape, no surrender, no mercy.</i>

1185
01:21:47,577 --> 01:21:51,317
<i>We gotta kill every last
rat bastard one of 'em.</i>

1186
01:21:51,384 --> 01:21:53,485
