1198
01:22:35,796 --> 01:22:39,987
<i>my warrior woman, my Valkyrie.</i>

1199
01:22:40,054 --> 01:22:42,836
<i>You'll always be mine.</i>

1200
01:22:42,903 --> 01:22:44,974
<i>Always...</i>

1201
01:22:45,051 --> 01:22:46,672
<i>and never.</i>

1202
01:22:59,638 --> 01:23:02,572
Evenin', officer.

1203
01:23:02,678 --> 01:23:07,463
I don't have to introduce myself, do I?
You read the papers.

