1248
01:25:48,846 --> 01:25:50,755
Don't visit me.

1249
01:25:50,831 --> 01:25:52,557
Don't write me.

1250
01:25:52,625 --> 01:25:54,734
Don't even say my name.

1251
01:25:55,156 --> 01:25:59,079
Maybe you won't let me visit,
but I'll still write to you, Hartigan.

1252
01:25:59,155 --> 01:26:01,064
I'll sign my letters "Cordelia. "

1253
01:26:01,620 --> 01:26:05,475
That's the name of a really cool
detective in books I read.

1254
01:26:05,552 --> 01:26:09,772
I'll write you every week... for forever.

1255
01:26:09,839 --> 01:26:12,524
Sure, kid.

1256
01:26:12,630 --> 01:26:14,634
Now, run on home.

1257
01:26:14,739 --> 01:26:16,974
It's not safe for you here.

1258
01:26:20,781 --> 01:26:23,466
Bye, Nancy.

1259
01:26:25,711 --> 01:26:27,945
I love you.

1260
01:26:35,857 --> 01:26:37,900
John Hartigan.

1261
01:26:38,705 --> 01:26:40,642
Mr. Law and Order.

1262
01:26:42,196 --> 01:26:44,977
Mr. By the Book.

1263
01:26:45,073 --> 01:26:47,145
Mr. High and Mighty.

1264
01:26:49,485 --> 01:26:52,688
I gotta give you credit, being such
a straight arrow for so damn many years

1265
01:26:52,755 --> 01:26:54,826
without it catching up with you.

1266
01:26:54,893 --> 01:26:58,029
