be getting any of, not in prison.

1274
01:27:26,579 --> 01:27:27,884
You hear me, Hartigan?

1275
01:27:27,951 --> 01:27:31,499
If you stop being stupid,
start playing along with us,

1276
01:27:31,566 --> 01:27:34,319
