1327
01:30:34,661 --> 01:30:39,552
<i>Nothing else matters -
not my life and not my pride, either.</i>

1328
01:30:39,629 --> 01:30:42,113
<i>It's only one final surrender they want.</i>

1329
01:30:42,189 --> 01:30:45,728
<i>You got me, Roark.
You beat me.</i>

1330
01:30:46,342 --> 01:30:49,794
<i>I say everything they want to hear,
just the way they want to hear it.</i>

1331
01:30:49,862 --> 01:30:53,161
<i>I tell them I'm a twisted.
Wretched child molester.</i>

1332
01:30:53,228 --> 01:30:56,488
<i>I agree to everything they want from me.</i>

1333
01:30:56,556 --> 01:30:58,531
<i>I love you, Nancy.</i>

1334
01:31:09,828 --> 01:31:12,418
It's a lot of miles into town, Hartigan.

1335
01:31:14,949 --> 01:31:19,361
- You care for a ride?
- Long as you stay in front of me.

1336
01:31:19,428 --> 01:31:23,178
