1337
01:31:23,245 --> 01:31:25,662
Christ.

1338
01:31:25,738 --> 01:31:28,452
Eight years.

1339
01:31:28,519 --> 01:31:31,684
Yeah.
Eight years.

1340
01:31:32,998 --> 01:31:35,846
Well, if it's any consolation to you...

1341
01:31:37,611 --> 01:31:39,711
you made me hate myself.

1342
01:31:42,118 --> 01:31:45,216
- Any word from Eileen?
