I'm sorry, John.

1345
01:31:55,592 --> 01:31:57,530
Don't be.

1346
01:31:57,606 --> 01:31:59,994
I'm glad.

1347
01:32:00,071 --> 01:32:03,140
Eileen always wanted kids.

1348
01:32:03,207 --> 01:32:05,058
She'll make a good mother.

1349
01:32:06,947 --> 01:32:11,109
Like you said, Bob -
water under the bridge.

1350
01:32:21,515 --> 01:32:24,737
<i>Bob and I get on
with our fond farewells to each other,</i>

1351
01:32:24,804 --> 01:32:28,832
<i>then I go looking for the only human being
on the planet who means a damn to me -</i>

1352
01:32:28,899 --> 01:32:30,242
<i>Nancy.</i>

1353
01:32:30,309 --> 01:32:33,627
<i>How could they have found out it was you
